  "active_lock_reason": null,
  "body": "### Component\r\n\r\nForge\r\n\r\n### Describe the feature you would like\r\n\r\nAn array of excluded globs would be very useful, e.g.:\r\n\r\n```toml\r\n[fmt]\r\nignore = ['**/vendor/*','**/preprocessed/*']\r\n```\r\n\r\nedit: for maximum flexibility, specify that patterns are applied in-order. That way, later negative patterns add exceptions to earlier positive patterns.\r\n\r\n### Additional context\r\n\r\n_No response_",
